!! UNTESTED ON OPENRC, HEADS UP !!
This repo contains ebuilds for GNOME 50.0, and its dependencies that are probably not in the main tree yet.

my ebuilds are not perfect, but they're good enough for me so, use at your own risk.

Tested on:
- Linux 7.0.0-rc3-next-20260313 (amd64)
- systemd 258.3

Note that I won't test it on OpenRC as I don't have a system that uses it as of now. Your mileage may vary.

They recently hardened their grip on systemd, so I do not know if it will even work with logind properly.

Pray for the GNOME devs in Gentoo.
I wish them good luck. This was a rough patch to begin with.